c8f43d45-bb0d-4297-a1ef-0c8507cc66b7.content:
Machine Learning Engineer — scikit-learn, feature engineering & model pipelines
Machine Learning Engineer with hands-on experience across supervised ML pipelines (SVM, Random Forest, regression), feature engineering, model evaluation, and a working knowledge of model deployment patterns.
Skills
Python, scikit-learn, NumPy, pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Feature Engineering, Model Evaluation, Regression, Classification, FastAPI/Flask, Jupyter
Experience
• Trained, validated and deployed supervised models (SVM, Random Forest, regression) for tasks including diabetes prediction, loan approval classification and house price regression.
• Built end-to-end ML experiments: data cleaning, feature engineering, hyperparameter tuning, and cross-validation in Jupyter notebooks.
• Packaged models as REST endpoints using FastAPI/Flask for inference and light production use.
• Evaluated model performance using precision/recall, ROC-AUC and regression metrics; iterated on feature sets to improve generalization.
• Implemented data visualizations and dashboards (Streamlit/Tableau) to communicate model insights to stakeholders.
Education
B.Tech in Computer Science & Engineering (AI & ML), Malla Reddy College of Engineering and Technology, Expected 2026
Certifications
Oracle Certified Data Science Professional, AWS Academy ML Foundations, IBM Data Fundamentals

7f11ed47-0b9a-4466-920b-e17a4d9d3cdb.title: AI_Engineer_Resume.docx
7f11ed47-0b9a-4466-920b-e17a4d9d3cdb.content:
AI Engineer — RAG & LLM systems, LangChain, FAISS, prompt engineering
AI Engineer focused on Generative AI and LLM systems: RAG architectures, prompt engineering, vector search (FAISS), LLM orchestration (LangChain/Ollama), and building GenAI endpoints and apps.
Skills
LangChain, FAISS, RAG, LLMs (Mistral), Ollama, Prompt Engineering, FastAPI, Streamlit, Docker, Git, Python, EdgeTTS, Whisper
Experience
• Built a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) Discord bot using LangChain + FAISS + Ollama (Mistral) to answer PDF-based queries with contextual LLM responses.
• Designed and deployed GenAI backend services (FastAPI) that orchestrate token-limited LLM calls, vector lookups and prompt templates for production features.
• Implemented end-to-end content generation pipeline integrating ChatGPT for script drafting, EdgeTTS for voice synthesis and Whisper for captions.
• Performed prompt engineering & testing, and iterated on retrieval/document chunking strategies to improve factuality and answer relevance.
• Packaged and modularized LLM components to enable easy model swapping and indexing improvements.
Education
B.Tech in Computer Science & Engineering (AI & ML), Malla Reddy College of Engineering and Technology, Expected 2026
Certifications
Oracle Generative AI Certified Professional, Google Prompt Design in Vertex AI, Google Develop GenAI Apps with Gemini & Streamlit

• Built interactive dashboards and prototypes using Streamlit/Tableau to surface model insights and evaluation metrics to stakeholders.
• Wrote SQL queries and MySQL scripts for dataset extraction, sampling and joining across normalized tables.
• Implemented basic ETL scripts and preprocessing pipelines to handle missing data, categorical encodings and normalization for ML tasks.
